#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:2
msgid "Nginx"
msgstr "Nginx"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:5
msgid "Fast-CGI关闭"
msgstr "Fast-CGI Disabled"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:6
msgid ""
"在Fast-CGI关闭的情况下， Nginx 仍然存在解析漏洞： 在文件路径(xx.jpg)后面加上 ``%00.php`` ， 即 "
"``xx.jpg%00.php`` 会被当做 php 文件来解析"
msgstr ""
"When Fast-CGI is disabled, Nginx still has a parsing vulnerability: "
"appending ``%00.php`` after a file path such as ``xx.jpg``, resulting in "
"``xx.jpg%00.php``, causes it to be parsed as a PHP file."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:10
msgid "Fast-CGI开启"
msgstr "Fast-CGI Enabled"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:11
msgid "在Fast-CGI开启状态下，在文件路径后加上 ``/xx.php`` ，则 ``xx.jpg/xx.php`` 会被解析为php文件"
msgstr ""
"When Fast-CGI is enabled, appending ``/xx.php`` to a file path causes "
"``xx.jpg/xx.php`` to be parsed as a PHP file."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:14
msgid "CVE-2013-4547"
msgstr "CVE-2013-4547"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:15
msgid "``a.jpg\\x20\\x00.php``"
msgstr "``a.jpg\\x20\\x00.php``"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:18
msgid "配置错误"
msgstr "Misconfiguration"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:21
msgid "目录穿越"
msgstr "Path Traversal"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:22
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"如果配置中存在类似 ``location /foo { alias /bar/; }`` 的配置时，``/foo../`` 会被解析为 "
"``/bar/../`` 从而导致目录穿越的发生。"
msgstr ""
"If the configuration contains a directive such as ``location /foo { alias "
"/bar/; }``, ``/foo../`` is parsed as ``/bar/../``, causing path traversal."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:25
msgid "目录遍历"
msgstr "Directory Listing"

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:26
msgid "配置中 ``autoindex on`` 开启时，Nginx中存在目录遍历漏洞。"
msgstr ""
"When ``autoindex on`` is enabled in the configuration, Nginx has a directory"
" listing vulnerability."

#: ../../source/vuln/middleware/nginx.rst:29
msgid "参考链接"
msgstr "References"

